{"tid":1756314,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"工會第一擊：不加班運動","createTime":"2019-11-26T03:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T03:41:26.000Z","uid":263648,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb6c51fd292ae4c77d5ac18a50d3b964e4d8a77","tid":1756314,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:35:53.000Z","msg":"我覺得我地而家吸納人，加入工會罷工個APPROACH遇到樽頸。<br />\n<br />\n搞工會，一定要吸納<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同業超過一半人</span></strong>先有得諗。如果一間公司十個人，得一、兩個人不合作運動，根本無用。唔可以只諗深黃，就算超淺黃都要吸納。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點做到多D人入工會呢? <br />\n<br />\n[拋下磚先] 其實文宣可以係: 有咗工會，<strong>可以發動<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不OT運動</span></span></strong>，每個月最後一個星期五一齊唔OT [再配合放工時間出席其他運動]，<strong><ins>做起點</ins></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要承認，香港人好鍾意返工; <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但無人鐘意OT</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n慢慢，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行動升級至每個星期五唔OT</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> --&gt; 之後升級到每星期，三日唔OT <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />--&gt; <strong><ins>之後升級到每日唔OT</ins></strong> --&gt; 即是<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">按章工作</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n你諗下，根本唔使升級至罷工，純粹按章工作，D老闆已經屌曬政府。變相，同行工時會變得合理。利用大企業老闆去屌政府。<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無違規，老闆又唔炒得員工</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n我明大家想罷工，但打呢個旗號，未必人人接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以拒絕加班號召，則人人都想</span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要幾個工會搞到呢種號召力，大家自然會爭住入其他工會。因為證明咗，工會<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有利無弊</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n之後? 只要夠多人，一話罷工一日，成行唔見咗人，仲得了? D老闆已經驚到仆街。由佢地屌林奠，事半功倍。"},{"pid":"ca65bc7b088cf92d8bac14b7e76ead43c07d942f","tid":1756314,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fb6c51fd292ae4c77d5ac18a50d3b964e4d8a77","tid":1756314,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:35:53.000Z","msg":"我覺得我地而家吸納人，加入工會罷工個APPROACH遇到樽頸。<br />\n<br />\n搞工會，一定要吸納<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同業超過一半人</span></strong>先有得諗。如果一間公司十個人，得一、兩個人不合作運動，根本無用。唔可以只諗深黃，就算超淺黃都要吸納。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點做到多D人入工會呢? <br />\n<br />\n[拋下磚先] 其實文宣可以係: 有咗工會，<strong>可以發動<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不OT運動</span></span></strong>，每個月最後一個星期五一齊唔OT [再配合放工時間出席其他運動]，<strong><ins>做起點</ins></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要承認，香港人好鍾意返工; <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但無人鐘意OT</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n慢慢，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行動升級至每個星期五唔OT</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> --&gt; 之後升級到每星期，三日唔OT <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />--&gt; <strong><ins>之後升級到每日唔OT</ins></strong> --&gt; 即是<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">按章工作</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n你諗下，根本唔使升級至罷工，純粹按章工作，D老闆已經屌曬政府。變相，同行工時會變得合理。利用大企業老闆去屌政府。<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無違規，老闆又唔炒得員工</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n我明大家想罷工，但打呢個旗號，未必人人接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以拒絕加班號召，則人人都想</span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要幾個工會搞到呢種號召力，大家自然會爭住入其他工會。因為證明咗，工會<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有利無弊</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n之後? 只要夠多人，一話罷工一日，成行唔見咗人，仲得了? D老闆已經驚到仆街。由佢地屌林奠，事半功倍。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:41:26.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到，請幫手推。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}